  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0cm 5.75pt 0cm 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>A large flightless bipedal avian race, Banoserit have
  short legs and exceptionally large hands on long arms.<span
  style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>Covered in feathers the Banoseri=
t are
  rarely seen without most of the body including their face covered in
  clothing.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Banoserit are mostly a dependable species who ho=
ld
  themselves and others to high morale values, reputation is exceptionally
  important to them.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>To be a Banoserit is to accept total responsibility =
for
  your own sins and the sins of your ancestors.<span
  style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>It is considered that if your
  ancestors did something morally bad that this behaviour is in your blood =
and
  you will accept the merciless judgement of your own species.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Banoserit are gifted with the most exceptional e=
yes of
  all species that now travel the stars.<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&n=
bsp;
  </span>They are able to see more than most other eyes are capable and a l=
arge
  part of their brain processes this sensory input.<span
  style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>The Banoserit are spending great
  effort to attempt to unlock this ability further for use in scanning the
  'skies' of space as an early warning system of danger.<span
  style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>This has led to the development =
of the
  Far Sight Center, considerably more effective than most Long Range Scanne=
rs.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Banoserit are found in large, and unusually vert=
ical
  cities in the deserts of the dryest planets.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-bottom:8.0pt'>The Banoserit preferre=
d weapon
  is the Phaser and they focus have a Balanced approach to Energy Research.=
</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
